version_description:
- Now supports logging in with your Discord account
- Many performance improvements
- Added light theme
- Added localization support (currently supports 13 languages)
- Added long description to bot pages
- Enhanced report feature
- Added a copy ID button
- Added lazy loading to bot search
- Bug fixes
- And much more!
